	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.75]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>you don't need high Cha or low Cha to fear a MOB.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Cha is used to determine how long the fear effect will last.  I have tested this with SKs, chanters and a rogues instill doubt.  All 3 didn't have a problem getting the fear spell to stick but when they had lower Cha, it would wear off sooner.  Add more Cha and the MOB would run forever.  well not forever.  why do you think a lot of rogues wear their iksar or DE illusion masks.  for the AC and MR?  Nope, they wear them for the 13Cha boost on it.  Helps ID a lot.  And until necros get a fear upgrade at lvl 29, chanters make the best fearers.  They get fear at 4 like necros and chase the moon at lvl 16.  1 step upgrade to fear.  and most chanters have a great cha stat.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
